P.text:
The Chairperson reviews, prepares, and issues on specific dates, following approval by the Secretary of Agriculture as provided by law (
7 U.S.C. 411a
) and Departmental Regulation, the official State and national estimates relating to crop production, livestock and livestock products, dairy and dairy products, poultry and poultry products, stocks of agricultural commodities, value of farm products, farm inputs, and other assigned agricultural aspects.
